name: Mamoru Miyano
about:
Hometown: Saitama, Japan\n
Height: 182 cm\n
Weight: 70 kg\n
Blood type: B\n
Hobbies: singing, soccer\n
Skills: harmonica, harp\n
\n
Mamoru Miyano won Best Voice Actor award in the Second Seiyuu Awards for leading roles of Kida Masaomi (Durarara!!), Setsuna F Seiei (Mobile Suit Gundam 00) and Hakugen Rikuson (Koutetsu Sangokushi). He married in late 2008; 2-3 months after his announcement, their son was born.\n
\n

Youtube: @Mamoru Miyano
